{
  "stem": "11296.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So mine job was I worked on the police station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I washed floors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I cleaned toilets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I did everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was young, and I was-- and I still, you know, believed I'm going to-- I'm going to be alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They cannot do nothing to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I worked every day from the beginning, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They assigned me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the ghetto was a committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this committee had to assign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans, they send in, they need so many, many people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- and the committee was called Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had to assign the people to every job what they're told them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my job was to go and clean the, you know, to wash the floors-- wash the floors, clean, wipe the windows-- anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we still found someplace we got a piece of bread from, you know, from the policemen, from the German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the one that-- you know-- another time, I went, you know-- this was in the-- late in the fall-- we went on the fields.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to dig the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We was working for a few miles, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we dig the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't take the potatoes home with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was all-- everything for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nice to put them together in bags and put them on-- on-- on trucks, and things like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this was the consistence, the time when I was in the ghetto, you know, between, you know-- I-- we saw to do some things, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was hanging people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The people who ran away, outside the ghetto they found people who were smuggling, bringing in stuff, you know, that they brought them in back to the-- to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Could you leave the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went a few times myself out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
